It’s absolutely mind-blowing! ❤❤❤

What makes this song truly amazing is the seamless transition from Farsi to Bangla, both in the singing and the music. 

And when Habib sings the line ‘jadu janehhh...’ it feels as though, under a lover’s spell, he has no energy left to say anything. 

It’s pure "Moha Jadu"!!!🫠
